    <title>github克隆项目失败</title>
    <url>/2022/07/29/github%E5%85%8B%E9%9A%86%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<div class="story post-story"><h2 id="unable-to-access-‘https-github-com-用户名-仓库名-git-39-SSL-certificate-problem-self问题解决"><a href="#unable-to-access-‘https-github-com-用户名-仓库名-git-39-SSL-certificate-problem-self问题解决" class="headerlink" title="unable to access ‘https://github.com/用户名/仓库名.git/&#39;: SSL certificate problem: self问题解决"></a>unable to access ‘<a href="https://github.com/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D/%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93%E5%90%8D.git/&#39;">https://github.com/用户名/仓库名.git/&#39;</a>: SSL certificate problem: self问题解决</h2><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><blockquote>
<p>今天想在github上找个项目玩玩，但是发现clone不下来，百度没有找到解决方案，于是又把git重装了一遍，发现还是不能clone,而且不能push，而且是同样的错误。于是Google了一下找到解决方案</p>
</blockquote>
</div><div class="story post-story"><h2 id="原因"><a href="#原因" class="headerlink" title="原因"></a>原因</h2><p>Git client in Fisheye&#x2F;Crucible server perform verification on the SSL certificate and stop the process if it is unknown.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>大概意思是：Fisheye&#x2F;Crucible服务器不能识别git的SSL证书，所以操作停止执行。</p>
</blockquote>
</div><div class="story post-story"><h2 id="解决"><a href="#解决" class="headerlink" title="解决"></a>解决</h2><ul>
<li>在git命令行输入以下命令即可</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global http.sslVerify false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</div>]]></content>
